---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Start" description="Begin your first path into Vaelinya.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Start</p>
    <h1>Begin your first path into Vaelinya.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Vaelinya is a colourful story world. Begin with the stories if you want the gentlest route in, then follow the world, language, and artefacts as they become useful.</p>
    <p>You do not need to learn the whole world first. Choose one door and start there.</p>
    <div class="link-list">
      <a href="/read/">Read a story</a>
      <a href="/world/">Explore the world</a>
      <a href="/language/">Learn a word</a>
      <a href="/artefacts/">Find an artefact</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
